# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-rollback-strategy
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document the authoritative rollback strategy for kernel deployments. This
#   ensures safe, predictable recovery from failed or unstable kernel releases.
#
# Rollback Strategy:
#
#   1. Identify Failure
#      - Review cluster-health.yml
#      - Check dmesg for kernel errors
#
#   2. Select Previous Kernel
#      - Use backup created by kernel-backup.yml
#
#   3. Deploy Previous Kernel
#      - ansible-playbook kernel-rollback.yml
#
#   4. Verify Recovery
#      - Run verification pipeline
#      - Confirm k3s workloads are stable
#
#   5. Document Incident
#      - Update kernel-rollback.log
#
# Notes:
#   - Rollback must be fast, safe, and fully automated.
# =============================================================================
